<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='154:180'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '017-1a' );" name="017-1a" class="pb">[017-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='180:188'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='188:196'>　禮書卷十七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='196:216'>　　　　　　　　　　　宋　陳祥道　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:242'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '017-2a' );" name="017-2a" class="pb">[017-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
